title: VA tantra lounge 3 (exotic sounds from the far east)
description:
Artist: Tantra Lounge 3 UPC: 05732
 
CD: Tantra Lounge 3 
Prepare to be taken deeper into Exotic Indian Electronica with Volume 3 in this remarkable series. This edition features some incredible remixes from cutting edge Electronica artists. Every track contributes to the genre-bending sound. Included are tracks and remixes by genre veterans Talvin Singh, Govinda, Ephemeral mists, Anoushka Shankar, Midival Punditz, Zohar, Donna De Lory and Omar Faruk Tekbilek.
